{"tid":2234762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人狗殊途 所謂修補警民關係 只係濫捕濫告地下化","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T15:48:15.000Z","uid":84408,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aed50dbd12ccf32ac9ae59b09fcdb3d0f93fd9d3","tid":2234762,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"策略上班狗係會將所有唔見得光嘅嘢地下化<br />\n交比國安公署去做<br />\n<br />\n門面上就會做到好足<br />\n比如響傳媒鏡頭前收斂<br />\n幫david擔遮<br />\n日後會開放遊行示威 但都係果種全部都係狗 比你行完就算果類<br />\n<br />\n但門面下打壓會更加勁<br />\n包括收集情報網 監視 轉為統戰類<br />\n<br />\n目的係將一啲想有自由但唔想犧牲（自己或他人）嘅人（唔一定和理非 勇武都可以有呢個心理）<br />\n接受呢個結果<br />\n<br />\n現階段可以做嘅嘢唔多 要靠國際戰線比壓力<br />\n因為香港響支共眼中仲有影響力同利益 所以會繼續比有限度自由香港"},{"pid":"92471f5ea0edc3cba463b47a99a6839c22fa59e0","tid":2234762,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"今時今日 討厭狗既只會繼續<br />\n撐狗既都係<br />\n<br />\n講出來個個會唔會太天真 以為仲有救？"},{"pid":"b5a1c58ed5c0f4865384e5128391953f9294f898","tid":2234762,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfce4e8947392f5d22057fbe236f729f02d551a","tid":2234762,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92471f5ea0edc3cba463b47a99a6839c22fa59e0","tid":2234762,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"今時今日 討厭狗既只會繼續<br />\n撐狗既都係<br />\n<br />\n講出來個個會唔會太天真 以為仲有救？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"就係有人咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f74c0e8f94a502230a97ad2e53704c4a54e6d8","tid":2234762,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src